<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar"></html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>لوحة التحكم للمشرف</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #2d48dfee, #350d91f5);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            background-color: #333;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }

        nav a ,nav div  {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin: 0 10px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, border-radius 0.3s ease;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            background-color: #444;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        main {
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        main p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            
        }
        
        .maindiv{
            
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: center;
        }



        .button {
            background-color: #007bff;
            background: #2d48dfee;

            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            margin: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 50px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            width: 200px;
            
          
        }
        .button i {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #720e8d;
        }

    @media (max-width: 568px) {
        nav {
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        nav a {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    
    .maindiv{
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;

        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }
    }


    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>لوحة التحكم للمشرف</h1>
    </header>

    <nav dir="rtl">
        <a href="/admin"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> الرئيسية</a>

        <div>
        <a href="/adminProfile"><i class="fas fa-user"></i>الحساب الشخصي</a>

        <a href="/api/auth/logout"><i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i>  الخروج</a>
    </div>
    </nav>

    <main dir="rtl" >
        <p>مرحبًا بك في صفحة المشرف!</p>
        <div class="maindiv">
        <a href="/adminAddFacture" class="button"><i class="fas fa-plus-square"></i> <span>اضافة فاتورة</span></a>
        <a href="/adminFacture" class="button"><i class="fas fa-file-invoice"></i> <span>الفواتير</span></a>
        <a href="/adminUsers" class="button"> <i class="fas fa-users"></i> <span>المستخدمين</span></a>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
